NR and together they\ncan be used to select preferred theoretical core-collapse supernova models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 1998 18:17:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 1999 17:35:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
